      <action-desc>
        <sponsor name-id="R000599">Mr. Ruiz</sponsor> (for himself and <cosponsor name-id="N000185">Mr. Nugent</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was referred to the <committee-name committee-id="HVR00">Committee on Veterans’ Affairs</committee-name>
